Exclusion criteria: Before calculating Customer Avoided Emissions, all Siemens

products, systems, solutions, services, and investments need to be checked against the following exclusion criteria:

→ Field of application: No Customer Avoided Emissions may be accounted for and reported in the military use or nuclear power application fields.

→ Objections and concerns of external stakeholders: If stakeholders express concerns or objections, internal or external information is evaluated and appropriate mea- sures are taken.